			Xazzt?  Are you the Xazzt from RZ?.. hehe<BR>
<BR>
Kimentari, I'm not gonna spoil it completely for ya, but here's hint.  Walk up to Gavel and type this...<BR>
<BR>
&quot;What about Galvanized?&quot;<BR>
<BR>
In reguards to the original topic, yes, the items you described that come off Bilge and Sludge are for the Chestplate, not the Gauntlets.  The Gauntlets of the Ardent are found by the following means:<BR>
<BR>
Babbinsbort, a Gnome Necromancer, lives on the 3rd floor in Befallen.  To get to his room, from the locked door going INTO the 3rd floor, turn right, make your first left, go through the door, straight across to the other side of room, through the archway, make a left, and go through that door.  To your left will be the corner where Babbinsbort will spawn.  You'll know it because there will be a fallen pillar between you and that corner.  Now comes the fun part.<BR>
<BR>
Babbinsbort is exactly a 7 hour and 5 minute spawn.  And here's the REAL kicker.  Almost every time, it will be a PLACEHOLDER (ghoul, skeleton, rat) instead of Babbinsbort.  I once witnessed every one of the spawns (I logged in every 7 hours and watched) for *3 DAYS STRAIGHT*, and for those 3 days, it was a placeholder EVERY TIME.<BR>
<BR>
5 quests down, 3 to go :).
